name: Good Morning, Mickey!
overview: Good Morning, Mickey!! is a television series on Disney Channel. It was one of The Disney Channel's first original programs. It featured classic Disney shorts. Although Mickey Mouse shorts, without surprise, were the primary programming, additional cartoons featuring Goofy, Donald Duck, Chip 'n' Dale, Pluto, and others were also shown. It was first aired on April 18, 1983. Its time-slot for its early run was at 7:30 AM Eastern Time, making it the second program of the Disney Channel's 16 hour programming day. It was followed by Donald Duck Presents.
